short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save current tab to local calendar

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save tab to local calendar so you can plan to actually follow up and read the webpage you were going to look into. It is done by downloading an ics file that you open in your calender of choice. You can also change the application icon to your favorit NFT or anything else if you want in the settings menu.
